## Phase 4: Sitemap Index Integration and robots.txt (addressed in Phase 1E and 1C)

Already covered above. The key points:
- Sitemap index at `/api/sitemap-index.xml` combines static and dynamic sitemaps
- robots.txt references the index and disallows authenticated routes
