---

## Phase 5: Additional SEO Enhancements (LOWER PRIORITY)

### 5A. Add `<meta name="googlebot" content="max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large">` to index.html

**File to modify:** `C:\Users\johnm\iskrib_v3\client\index.html`

