3. **Meta tag verification:** View page source on a post page and verify `<title>`, `<meta name="description">`, `og:title`, etc. contain actual post content rather than generic text.
4. **Profile URL verification:** Navigate to `/user/{someUserId}` -- should render the profile page. Navigate to `/visitProfile?userId={someUserId}` -- should also still work.
5. **Rich results test:** Use Google's Rich Results Test (https://search.google.com/test/rich-results) on a post URL to verify Article JSON-LD is valid.

